1. *Stara* je zadovoljna svojim unukom. (Grandma is pleased with her grandson.)
2. On se dobro slaže sa svojom *starom*. (He gets along well with his grandmother.)
3. Bojali smo se da će *stara* biti ljuta. (We were afraid that grandmother would be angry.) 
4. Ona je *stara* baka. (She is an old grandmother.)
5. Istorija je *stara* nauka. (History is an old science.) 
6. Ona voli da čuva *stare* stvari. (She likes to keep old things.)